"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-13-China-to-send-405-athletes-to-2024-Summer-Olympic-Games-in-Paris-1vclmKHiBoY-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  The roster of Team China for the 2024 Summer Olympic Games in Paris is confirmed in Beijing, July 13, 2024.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 241, \"end\": 251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_at_the_2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999996470906521, \"rank\": 3.520057434989665e-07, \"text\": \"Team China\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_at_the_2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_at_the_2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 289, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999980995269067, \"rank\": 1.9004767227884207e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 311, \"end\": 318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999998638793478, \"rank\": 1.3612075932216986e-07, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CMG  The roster of Team China for the 2024 Summer Olympic Games in Paris was confirmed on Saturday.\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 435, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_at_the_2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999996470906521, \"rank\": 3.520057434989665e-07, \"text\": \"Team China\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_at_the_2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_at_the_2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 403, \"end\": 408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999980995269067, \"rank\": 1.9004767227884207e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A total of 405 athletes, including 136 males and 269 females, will participate in the Olympic Games that will begin on July 26.\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Forty-two of the athletes are Olympic gold medalists and 223 of them will be making their Olympic debut in Paris.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 672, \"end\": 677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999980995269067, \"rank\": 1.9004767227884207e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Twenty-six of the athletes are of ethnic minority groups.\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 736, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The average age of the team is 25 years old.\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 781, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The team will be competing in 236 events of 42 disciplines across 30 sports at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A total of 311 working staff, including 42 foreigners, will be assisting them on training, coaching and other fronts.\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thirty-four of these foreigners are coaches.\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1044, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"China won a total of 89 medals, including 38 golds, 32 silvers and 19 bronzes at the 2020 Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1046, \"end\": 1051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9534832597191522, \"rank\": 0.0471075534274571, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1413, \"entities\": []}]}"